# GrantConnect Opportunity Contacts

Daily scrape of current grant opportunities and contact email addresses from
[grants.gov.au](https://www.grants.gov.au/Go/List) (GrantConnect).

**Live dashboard:** https://nick-claude-agents.github.io/au-gov-grants/

Runs automatically at 5:00 AM AEST via GitHub Actions. New opportunities and new
contacts are highlighted in each run, and a daily summary email is sent with the
Excel registry attached.

Sister project to [au-gov-tenders](https://github.com/nick-claude-agents/au-gov-tenders)
(AusTender) and [au-gov-buyict](https://github.com/nick-claude-agents/au-gov-buyict).
